Class MarketCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.ps18.model.board.boardcells.MarketCell

  • public class MarketCell
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines a market cell.
    When a family member is placed, MarketCell activates a set of quick effects.
